data.description: Welcome to the stunning property! This beautiful home offers a spacious 2,467 sq ft of living space with 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. The bonus room upstairs provides additional versatility for your lifestyle needs. Enjoy the convenience of an inground pool perfect for those hot summer days. The property is equipped with solar panels, allowing for energy efficiency and cost savings. The presence of a generator ensures uninterrupted power supply during unexpected outages. Maintaining a lush outdoor oasis is made easy with the sprinkler system that is connected to a well. Additionally, a workshop is available for those who enjoy DIY projects or need additional storage space. Built in 2007, this home combines modern features with added amenities, making it the perfect place to call home.
